# Durcissement SSH — bye-google (roles/hardening)
PermitRootLogin prohibit-password
PubkeyAuthentication yes
PasswordAuthentication {{ 'no' if ssh_disable_password | bool else 'yes' }}
KbdInteractiveAuthentication {{ 'no' if ssh_disable_password | bool else 'yes' }}
PermitEmptyPasswords no
X11Forwarding no
MaxAuthTries 3
LoginGraceTime 30
ClientAliveInterval 300
ClientAliveCountMax 2
AllowAgentForwarding no
